column1: UPDATE I_BPartner i  SET SalesRep_ID=(SELECT AD_User_ID FROM AD_User u  WHERE EXISTS (SELECT salesrep_id FROM C_BPARTNER BP WHERE u.C_BPARTNER_ID=BP.C_BPARTNER_ID AND BP.ISSALESREP='Y')  AND u.Value=i.SalesRepValue AND u.AD_Client_ID=i.AD_Client_ID)  WHERE I_IsImported='N' AND i.SalesRepValue IS NOT NULL AND AD_Client_ID=1000002
